Entries.default: "Feels real sticky. Like something breathing on your neck."
"It seems we've all been marked Champions of the Hunt."
"Mind your step, Watcher. This place bears the marks of the gods."
"I notice we have not visited my mother's realm. Still nervous about upsetting her favorite son?"
"Shit, cap, this place feels thrice-stuffed with anguished souls."
"Complanca, what a mess. I thought gods would keep the Beyond tidier."
"Do you think we will find another who speaks my language? Like before? I want to hear it again."
